songs.title: In My Room
songs.lyrics:
There's a world where
I can go and
Tell my secrets too
In my room. (Bis)

In this world I lock out all my
Worrys and my fears

In my room (Bis)
In my room (Bis)

Do my dreaming and I'm skeaming
Lie awake and pray
Do my crying and my sighting
Laugh at yesterday...

Parapapapapa
Que es lo que pasa contigo
Que vas siempre ahí. (Bis)

There's a world whereI can go and
Tell my secrets to

In my room.(Bis)

Do my dreaming and I'm skeaming
Lie awake and pray
Do my crying and my sightin
Laugh at yesterday...

Parapapapapa
Que es lo que pasa contigo
Que vas siempre ahí. (Bis)

Now is dark and
I'm alone but
I won't be afraid
In my room
